inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-subnet-tags-nodeLaunchConfiguration-cdb8159
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-0515e383139bd64f0","subnet-0bf01616e0c5556a5","subnet-0ccde08977d88d72b"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-ea93edd-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-ea93edd
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
